`BitNet-MLX` is an edge-native mathematical compiler, optimization engine, and training framework designed by JuniorCloud LLC. It bypasses heavy server framing to offer direct, bare-metal acceleration on Apple's Matrix Coprocessor (AMX) via the Unified Memory Architecture (UMA).\
